		<%= link_to "Project Management ", page_path('projmgt') %> and
		<%= link_to "Business Management ", page_path('bizops') %>, an IT department can run quite successfully.
	</p>
	<%= image_tag("SM and proj 2b.png",:size => '450x320', alt: "IT Mgt"  )%>

